## Quick Start

```bash
source .venv/bin/activate        # ALWAYS use the venv
make test                         # 236 tests, all must pass (uses OMEGA_ENV=test mock)
make lint                         # flake8 code quality check
make demo                         # End-to-end demo (graceful degradation if no backend)
make health                       # Provider & model dashboard
make repl                         # Interactive REPL
make pr-ready                     # Verify all PR gate requirements
PYTHONPATH=src python3 -m pytest tests/  # Live inference (requires lmster :1234)
```

