## Architecture — Sovereign Loop

```
Query → TriageRouter → HealthMonitor → ModelGateway → Response → Memory → Soul Update
```

## Tiered Research Pipeline (Investigative Journalism Model)

```
L1 Intern  (Qwen3-1.7B) → Raw data packets. NO analysis. Just gather.
L2 Assistant (Gemma 4 31B) → Synthesize. Flag uncertainties. Write memo.
L3 Senior (Big Pickle) → Resolve uncertainties. Final report + improvement briefs.

L2 + L3 share the same OpenCode session -- mode/agent/subagent/tier tracked in observability.
```

