## Testing Rules

- **Mock mode**: `make test` — OfflineMockBackend (~2s, 236 tests)
- **Live mode**: `PYTHONPATH=src python3 -m pytest tests/` — requires lmster with model loaded (~3-4min)
- **NEVER use `--break-system-packages`**. Always: `source .venv/bin/activate`

## Hardware Constraints

- **CPU**: AMD Ryzen 7 5700U (Zen 2, 8C/16T, AVX2, no AVX-512)
- **RAM**: 14Gi total (~2Gi overhead → ~12Gi for AI)
- **GPU**: None (integrated only, CPU-only inference)
- **Models**: `/media/arcana-novai/omega_library/models/gguf/`
- **Concurrency**: ResourceGuard (Semaphore(1)) — ONE model at a time. Do not bypass.

